</head>
<body data-scroll-container>

    <div class="transition-overlay">
        <div class="overlay-column"></div>
        <div class="overlay-column"></div>
        <div class="overlay-column"></div>
    </div>

    <section class="story-hero" data-scroll-section>
        <div class="hero-content">
            <h1 data-scroll data-scroll-speed="2">Legacy of <span>Excellence</span></h1>
            <p data-scroll data-scroll-speed="1">Since 2008, shaping the future of technical education in Bangladesh.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="scroll-down">
            <i class="ri-arrow-down-line"></i>
        </div>
    </section>

    <section class="story-details" data-scroll-section>
        <div class="container">
            <div class="story-grid">
                <div class="story-image" data-scroll data-scroll-speed="1.5">
                    <img src="/images/frontOfCollege.jpg" alt="Magura Polytechnic Institute Campus">
                    <div class="experience-badge">15+ Years</div>
                </div>
                <div class="story-text">
                    <h2 class="reveal-text">The Beginning of a Journey</h2>
                    <p>Established in **2008**, Magura Polytechnic Institute (MPI) started its journey with a vision to provide world-class technical skills to the youth of Bangladesh. Located in the heart of Magura, it has become a beacon of hope for thousands of aspiring engineers.</p>
                    <p>Starting with only 4 basic technologies, we have expanded into a massive campus with modern laboratories, a rich library, and highly qualified instructors dedicated to building the nation.</p>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </section>

    <section class="stats-section" data-scroll-section>
        <div class="stat-item" data-scroll data-scroll-direction="horizontal" data-scroll-speed="2">
            <h3>2000+</h3>
            <span>Students</span>
        </div>
        <div class="stat-item" data-scroll data-scroll-direction="horizontal" data-scroll-speed="-2">
            <h3>50+</h3>
            <span>Experts</span>
        </div>
        <div class="stat-item" data-scroll data-scroll-direction="horizontal" data-scroll-speed="3">
            <h3>07</h3>
            <span>Technologies</span>
        </div>
    </section>

    <section class="timeline-section" data-scroll-section>
        <h2 class="section-title">Academic Evolution</h2>
        <div class="timeline">
            <div class="timeline-card left">
                <div class="card-inner">
                    <h4>2008</h4>
                    <p>MPI was founded by the Government of Bangladesh to empower rural technical talent.</p>
                </div>
            </div>
            <div class="timeline-card right">
                <div class="card-inner">
                    <h4>Current Status</h4>
                    <p>Offering Computer, Electronics, Electrical, Civil, Refrigeration & Air-Conditioning, Food, and Power technology.</p>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </section>

    <section class="cta-story" data-scroll-section>
        <h2>Be a Part of Our Future</h2>
        <a href="/signup" class="btn-primary">Join MPI Today</a>
    </section>

